             was indicted for <rs id="t18270913-162-off921" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18270913-162-off921" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18270913-162-off921" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the 5th of September, 1 purse, value 1d., and 9 shillings., the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18270913-162-victim1599" type="victimName">
                           Richard 
                           Gee
                        <interp inst="t18270913-162-victim1599" type="surname" value="Gee"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18270913-162-victim1599" type="given" value="Richard"></interp>
